OL,3,CBritain's 'biggest drug smuggling
OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FA gang which smuggled drugs on an
OL,7,F"industrial and unprecedented scale"
OL,8,Ftotalling up to #7 billion and
OL,9,Fweighing as much as 30 family sized
OL,10,Fcars have finally been jailed after
OL,11,FBritain's longest-running criminal
OL,12,Ftrial.
OL,14,FEighteen members of the international
OL,15,Forganised crime group (OCG) have been
OL,16,Fconvicted of importing heroin, cocaine
OL,17,Fand cannabis to the UK over two-and-a-
OL,18,Fhalf years.
