OL,3,CBritain's 'biggest drug smuggling
OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FThe gang, based largely in the North
OL,7,FWest, covered from the South of
OL,8,FEngland to Scotland, importing drugs
OL,9,Ffrom the Netherlands and storing them
OL,10,Fin warehouses.
OL,12,FThe stash would be hidden in strong
OL,13,Fsmelling foods such as onions, garlic
OL,14,Fand ginger, with offenders using
OL,15,Fencrypted communications, faked
OL,16,Fdocuments and even changing their
OL,17,Fnames by deed poll to import the drugs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
