OL,3,CBritain's 'biggest drug smuggling
OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FBut it was eventually brought down
OL,7,Fafter an innocent lorry driver
OL,8,Fsuspected criminal activity, and
OL,9,Fcalled the police, leading the
OL,10,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) to begin
OL,11,Fits investigation and uncover the UK's
OL,12,Fbiggest ever detected drugs conspiracy.
OL,14,FThe case was so big, two criminal
OL,15,Ftrials were needed to try the
OL,16,Fdefendants, with one lasting 23
OL,17,Fmonths, a record in England and Wales,
OL,18,Fand the other nine months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
