OL,3,CBritain's 'biggest drug smuggling
OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FIt can finally be reported after the
OL,7,Flast three men, all from the North
OL,8,FWest, were found guilty and reporting
OL,9,Frestrictions were lifted.
OL,11,FThe judge who presided over the trials
OL,12,Fsaid the drug smuggling was "on an
OL,13,Findustrial and hitherto unprecedented
OL,14,Fscale".
OL,16,FManchester Crown Court heard how only
OL,17,Fsix seizures of drugs, with a total
OL,18,Fstreet value of #40million, were made
OL,19,Ffrom the OCG between August 2015 and
OL,20,FSeptember 2018.
