OL,3,CBritain's 'biggest drug smuggling
OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FBut NCA investigators proved there
OL,7,Fwere at least 240 importations, which
OL,8,Fwent to great lengths to confuse the
OL,9,Fauthorities and avoid justice.
OL,11,FTrial judge Paul Lawton said if only
OL,12,Fhalf of the importations contained the
OL,13,Fsame quantities of drugs as the six
OL,14,Frecovered seizures, it would amount to
OL,15,F#3billion worth.
OL,17,FRingleader Paul Green, 59, known as
OL,18,FThe Big Fella, was the point of
OL,19,Fcontact for numerous OCGs who paid a
OL,20,Ffee to ship heroin, cocaine,
OL,21,Famphetamines and cannabis into the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
