OL,3,CBritain's 'biggest drug smuggling
OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FThe crime group bought so many onions
OL,7,F- between 40 tonnes and 50 tonnes a
OL,8,Fweek, that it could not get rid of
OL,9,Fthem and often sent them back to the
OL,10,Fcontinent to act as another cover
OL,11,Fload, the court was told.
OL,13,FProsecutor Andrew Thomas KC said a
OL,14,Ffeature of the sequence of
OL,15,Fconspiracies between March 2016 and
OL,16,FSeptember 2018 was the "determination
OL,17,Fto continue the importations even
OL,18,Fafter arrests and/or drug seizures".
