OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FHe told jurors: "As soon as one
OL,7,Fcompany became exposed, they would
OL,8,Fswitch to another one."
OL,10,FAmong the many items of evidence
OL,11,Fgathered were messages on Green's
OL,12,Fencrypted Encrochat phone, with his
OL,13,Fhandler name of "Duckfarmer", to
OL,14,Faccomplices in which he arranged
OL,15,Fshipments.
