OL,3,CBritain's 'biggest drug smuggling
OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FGreen, 59, had no previous convictions
OL,7,Fbut had changed his name twice by deed
OL,8,Fpoll from Simon Swift to James Russell
OL,9,Fand then to Green due to financial
OL,10,Fdifficulties and his self-confessed
OL,11,Finvolvement in property and business
OL,12,Ffraud.
OL,14,FAs well as his OCG customers, Green
OL,15,Falso brought in drugs for his own gang
OL,16,Fto distribute for sale.
