OL,4,Cgang' jailed
OL,6,FSentencing, Judge Paul Lawton told
OL,7,Fgang members: "Your main purpose was
OL,8,Fthe importation of controlled drugs on
OL,9,Fan international, and hitherto
OL,10,Funprecedented, scale with a value of
OL,11,Fat least #2 billion and potentially as
OL,12,Fhigh as #7 billion.
OL,14,F"The harm caused beyond the
OL,15,Fimportation is incalculable.
OL,17,F"What you were actually distributing
OL,18,Fwas addiction, misery, social
OL,19,Fdegradation and death."
OL,21,FWhat were some of the sentences?
