OL,6,FRichard Harrison, NCA regional head of
OL,7,Finvestigations, said: "This was an
OL,8,Fextremely high-harm OCG that used
OL,9,Fevery tactic possible to evade
OL,10,Fdetection and cheat justice.
OL,12,F"The offenders smuggled huge
OL,13,Fquantities of drugs into the UK. They
OL,14,Fhad absolutely no ethics. They stooped
OL,15,Fincredibly low and left a trail of
OL,16,Fdevastation for entirely innocent
OL,17,Fpeople by cloning businesses and
OL,18,Fstealing identities.
